Interface RulePhaseExecutionStatisticsModel

  • All Superinterfaces:
    com.tinkerpop.frames.VertexFrame, WindupVertexFrame

    public interface RulePhaseExecutionStatisticsModel
extends WindupVertexFrame
    This stores the time it takes to execute all of the rules within a particular phase of execution.
